# meraki_wireless_ethernet_port_profile_default (Data Source)

This data source can read the `Wireless Ethernet Port Profile Default` configuration.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "meraki_wireless_ethernet_port_profile_default" "example" {
  network_id = "L_123456"
}
```
